Name: $IMP_ID
Description: Unique click ID - this may be used as a cachebuster, and may be returned to InMobi by third-party conversion trackers to report a conversion. This will be of a format like this: 83f47f85-3c3c-4beb-a42e-b608b97a2c40

Name: $IMP_TS
Description: Numeric timestamp, not recorded in logs

Name: $BLINDED_SITE_ID
Description: Sub publisher macro - This would be an unique id for the site on which the ad would be shown
